ign=left class=m><span class=title> How to look dashing and be impressive.</span><hr size=1> Last night, I got bored with the constant hunting. After getting my tunic back from a friend (had to go two weeks tunicless in battle :P), I discussed the rumored, &quot;Happy Love Bracers&quot; with him. He was interested, and so was I. We were already in South Ro, so I decided to start walking. Before that, I realized he still had my 450p which he was working with trades on...<br>
<br>
Wanting to freak out the nearby level 50 DE cleric, I said, &quot;Hey Druid, don't forget you still owe me that 450p&quot;<br>
Druid: &quot;Want to roll for 50p?&quot;<br>
&quot;Sure.&quot; I win the roll. Of course, no money exchanges hands, he still owes me just the 450p, we're just working up the situation. Druid seems upset at now having to owe me 500p.<br>
&quot;Say, Druid... you interested in keeping that 500p?&quot;<br>
Druid: &quot;Sure&quot;<br>
&quot;Roll for it.&quot; He 'wins' *whew*.<br>
&quot;See you around.&quot; I start running off to Neriak. The cleric is stunned. After a few moments, he decides to take up betting with druid.<br>
<br>
Long story short, druid loses the 500p, then gains 600p, then a total of 1200p, then a total of 4000p, but then owes 500kp.<br>
<br>
I don't know if the cleric intended to pay the 4kp, but I'm sure he's not gonna be able to get the 500kp from my druid friend, heh.<br>
<br>
So after I get to Neriak, the druid gets there. We hang around the tops of the walls of 3rd Gate for a while, until Ratraz shows up. Against a 20 druid and 24 rogue, he stood no chance. I got a bracer, my druid friend got a bracer, and one of the druid's friends got a bracer.<br>
<br>
Green plate bracers just look so dang cool. If you're ever bored, you might consider getting a bracer for yourself.<br>
<br>
Also, he's ok exp, he spawns at an ok interval, but he takes a long time to get to the rooftops. I haven't tried attacking him in the bar, so I don't know if the others around him would defend him, being merchants and a rogue (who dislikes Ratraz). Every single time you kill him, you've got a guaranteed bracer, troll head, warclub (@5p), and sometimes other goodies. Other people have claimed to receive massive faction hits with Dark Bargainers, and even Ratraz says that DB's will get revenge. I don't know, maybe it was just from people killing him over and over, but I did not notice any significant faction drops, and I didn't see a faction message. Black and dark green look soooo good together. Maybe I'll get a militia tunic and make myself a X-mas suit for next year :P. <p>Woof woof woof!<br>
Berdusk Ravenspike,<br>
of the Barking Mice.</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=298.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=308.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.emailToFriend?topicID=309.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.threadControl?topicID=309.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=309.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=309.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesafehousetherootcellar">The Root Cellar<option value="thesafehouselaboratory">Laboratory<option value="thesafehousefrm15">